About

We are Vasai-Virar

This is an unofficial dashboard for the COVID-19 cases in Vasai-Virar area.

We are a team of individuals from Vasai-Virar who thought that we need a dashboard for tracking the spread of Novel Coronavirus in our area.

Disclaimer

Important Notes

#. This is a crowd sourced tracker and will be updated once we have a confirmation on the case from an official datasource.

#. Official datasource here means the bulletins from VVCMC and the Collectors Office and Official Social Media handles.

#. Please do not believe in rumours and do not contribute to rumours. Follow the guidelines issued by VVCMC.

Notes

  1. Officially, VVCMC is not counting the death of #32 on the list, the 25 year old from Cancer patient from Papdy who died in Mumbai, we are counting it since he was a Vasaikar. There is also another patient that VVCMC is not counting, but we are.
  2. The details for the Recovered patients is not shared by VVCMC, hence we do not have an update on the table that we have above. Once we have the data, we will update the table.
  3. The numbers for Total Tested and Under Quarantine are taken from the VVCMC Dashboard.
  4. VVCMC Note Dated 4th July : There has been a variable increase in the progressive number of Covid positive patients of Vasai-Virar city municipal corporation in the last few days owing to the addition of some cases from the first two weeks of June 2020 who were admitted and even discharged after treatment as per protocols. As some cases being referred from private setups or from other districts/municipal corporations need verification before adding them to the total count of our patients, 898 cases have been verified over the last few days and then collectively been added to the line list of Covid positive patients of Vasai-Virar City Municipal Corporation and the total line list now amounts to 5959 cases.
